'''Kate Vernon''' (born c. [[1961]]) is a [[Canada|Canadian]]-born film and television [[actress]]. She is best known for her role as Lorraine Prescott on the [[CBS]] [[soap opera]] ''[[Falcon Crest]]'' from (1984â€“1985), and for her role as the stuck-up and popular Benny Hanson in the [[comedy film]] ''[[Pretty in Pink]]'' (1986).

Vernon was briefly a regular on ''[[Who's the Boss?]]'' in [[1990]] as a girlfriend of Tony Micelli ([[Tony Danza]]). Most recently, Vernon has played the scheming [[Lady Macbeth]]-like [[Ellen Tigh]] on ''[[Battlestar Galactica (2004 TV series)|Battlestar Galactica]]''. In 1994 she starred in [[Dangerous Touch]] along with Lou Diamond Phillips. 

Her father was actor [[John Vernon]], and her sister is singer/actress [[Nan Vernon]].

